OK, FoxFingers went through a door that led down to the brig. See, 
the floor they were on was circular and had three passsage ways that 
went down into the ship. FoxFingers took one passage that went 
through part of the ships engine rooms, then on down to the brig.

And yes, to keep it interesting, FF is going to pass part of the 
engine room, life support and some minor propulsion systems before 
getting to the brig.
